OL,3,CTeen who suffered brain injury while
OL,4,Cplaying rugby makes amazing recovery
OL,6,FDylan Morgan is an ordinary teenager
OL,7,Fwith an extraordinary story.
OL,9,FEighteen months ago he was playing for
OL,10,FBargoed under-13s against Monmouth
OL,11,Fwhen he took a knock to the head.
OL,13,FInitially he was treated for
OL,14,Fconcussion and showed no symptoms, so
OL,15,Fhe was allowed to continue.
OL,17,FThe full-back carried on playing, not
OL,18,Fmaking contact with the ball again,
OL,19,Fbut something was awry.
