OL,3,CTeen who suffered brain injury while
OL,4,Cplaying rugby makes amazing recovery
OL,6,FHis father, Chris, who is also one of
OL,7,Fthe coaches, noticed his son just
OL,8,F"wandering" around the field, not
OL,9,Fengaged in the game at all.
OL,11,FThen he let a ball-carrier simply run
OL,12,Fpast him and did nothing to prevent a
OL,13,Ftry being scored.
OL,15,FDad Chris told ITV Cymru Wales: "I was
OL,16,Fthinking that's strange and it's not
OL,17,Flike Dylan. I actually said something
OL,18,Fthat will haunt me because it could
OL,19,Fhave been the last thing I'd ever say
OL,20,Fto him.
