OL,6,F"I said: 'Dylan, listen, if you ain't
OL,7,Fgonna try then there are boys on the
OL,8,Fside that want to get on'.
OL,10,F"And he went behind the posts with the
OL,11,Fboys and he was just wobbling a little
OL,12,Fbit. So, I went over and spoke to him
OL,13,Fand he was just looking through me,
OL,14,Fthere was no emotion in his eyes."
OL,16,FAn ambulance was called but Dylan's
OL,17,Fcondition was deteriorating. He was
OL,18,Fvomiting and now admits himself that
OL,19,Fhe was struggling to keep his eyes
OL,20,Fopen at times.
