OL,6,FThen a chain of events fell into place
OL,7,Fthat would save his life.
OL,9,FFirst of all, an army medic was on the
OL,10,FMonmouth touchline. He came over and
OL,11,Fasked to assess Dylan. The medic
OL,12,Fidentified that Dylan's condition was
OL,13,Fworsening at an alarming rate, so they
OL,14,Fcalled 999 again to drive home the
OL,15,Fseverity of the situation.
