OL,6,FDylan was initially bound for the
OL,7,FGrange Hospital in Cwmbran but one of
OL,8,Fthe medical professionals who attended
OL,9,Fthe scene happened to be a neuro-
OL,10,Fspecialist. The decision was then made
OL,11,Fto take Dylan straight to specialist
OL,12,Fcare at the University Hospital of
OL,13,FWales in Cardiff.
OL,15,FThe neurosurgeon who was on-call that
OL,16,Fday at the Heath also happened to be
OL,17,Fat the hospital visiting somebody.
OL,19,FEverything fell into place to make
OL,20,Fsure Dylan received the right care in
OL,21,Fthe right place.
