OL,3,CTeen who suffered brain injury while
OL,4,Cplaying rugby makes amazing recovery
OL,6,FBy the time Dylan arrived at the
OL,7,Fhospital, he no longer had the use of
OL,8,Fthe left side of his body and was put
OL,9,Finto an induced coma.
OL,11,FChris was joined by his wife as their
OL,12,Fson was being prepared for surgery. It
OL,13,Fhad become apparent that Dylan had a
OL,14,Fbleed on the brain.
OL,16,FThe parents were told to prepare for
OL,17,Fthe possibility their son would not
OL,18,Fsurvive the four-hour operation.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/13
