OL,3,CTeen who suffered brain injury while
OL,4,Cplaying rugby makes amazing recovery
OL,6,F"After an hour and a half, a nurse
OL,7,Fcame to get us and took us down
OL,8,Fthrough the basement of the hospital,"
OL,9,FChris recalls.
OL,11,F"I can remember saying to my wife:
OL,12,F'he's gone. He's died'.
OL,14,F"They told us four hours, and an hour
OL,15,Fand a half later they're calling for
OL,16,Fus. I just felt sick."
OL,18,FDylan was still in surgery and his
OL,19,Fparents were simply being taken to a
OL,20,Fseparate waiting room.
