OL,6,FAfter an agonising wait, his parents
OL,7,Flearned surgery had gone well. An
OL,8,Funderlying condition called AVM -
OL,9,Fwhich is the tangling of blood vessels
OL,10,Fin the brain - had caused the bleed.
OL,12,FTo relieve the pressure, part of
OL,13,FDylan's skull was removed and inserted
OL,14,Finto his abdomen to keep the bone
OL,15,Falive, where it stayed for five months
OL,16,Fbefore Dylan underwent a second
OL,17,Foperation to put the bone back.
