OL,6,F"It was just a funny feeling," Dylan
OL,7,Ftells us. "It was just there (in my
OL,8,Fstomach). I could play with it, touch
OL,9,Fit. It was just wild."
OL,11,FFast forward to the present day and
OL,12,FDylan is back playing rugby.
OL,14,FLast month, Bargoed faced Monmouth -
OL,15,Fthe same opposition as on the day of
OL,16,Fthe incident - in a charity match at
OL,17,FRodney Parade.
OL,19,FThe game was restarted at the same
OL,20,Ftime and score as when it was
OL,21,Foriginally called off.
