OL,4,Cplaying rugby makes amazing recovery
OL,6,FChris insists he has no concern over
OL,7,Fhis son going back onto the field now
OL,8,Fthat the AVM has been removed and his
OL,9,Fskull fused back together.
OL,11,FDylan will now undergo a scan every
OL,12,Fyear to check that the condition has
OL,13,Fnot returned.
OL,15,F"Most of the parents were in tears
OL,16,Fbecause they'd gone through it with
OL,17,Fus, to be fair," Chris says of the day
OL,18,Fhis son returned to the field.
